==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[vapor]] [[pressure]]''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]''; ''plural:'' '''vapor pressures''')

#{{physics}} The [[pressure]] that a [[vapor]] [[exerts]], or the [[partial pressure]] if it is mixed with other gases.
